{"id":"223de658-41a9-4b52-9071-34ed499818e7","name":"Toya Todoroki / Dabi","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JGe3Nfdbi0vAedaw4wh4t.gif\" style=\"width: auto; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Toya Todoroki / Dabi | My Hero Academia<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQh_LBnc37m3VmKHVRO9H.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><em>Dabi comes to our world! Well, not willingly.<br>When a League of Villains' mission goes sideways, Dabi gets hit with a rival villain's portal summoning Quirk, sending Dabi falling into your seemingly normal life. He's going to need your help to get back.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ｏｐｔｉｏｎａｌ Ｂａｃｋｇｒｏｕｎｄ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xdOhqyIeo-Z2ef7-L3QRP.webp\" style=\"width: 400px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQh_LBnc37m3VmKHVRO9H.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616);\"><strong>𝖸𝗈𝗎 𝖼𝖺𝗇 𝗆𝖺𝗄𝖾 𝗋𝖾𝗊𝗎𝖾𝗌𝗍𝗌 𝖻𝗒 𝗀𝗈𝗂𝗇𝗀 𝗍𝗈 𝗆𝗒 </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ab8b41e0-1424-49fa-8d05-edb57f5fd8d8_character-requests\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(172, 164, 255, 0.616);\"><strong><u>𝖱𝖾𝗊𝗎𝖾𝗌𝗍 𝖡𝗈𝗍 𝗁𝖾𝗋𝖾</u></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616);\"><strong>!</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 63, 63, 0.616);\">𝓛𝓸𝓿𝓮 𝔂'𝓪𝓵𝓵,</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 63, 63, 0.616);\">𝔁𝓸𝔁𝓸</span></p><hr><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/5jUOuMBnav0iyM6DINhETm?si=2ce257b304e7436a\" target=\"_blank\">Toya's Song</a><br>𝖺𝗇𝗒 𝗉𝗈𝗏 (M4A